body.description: The ASUS ProArt B760-CREATOR D4 perfects the art of performance, empowering creativity and maximizing the computing power of the latest 12th&13th Generation Intel® Core™ processors with powerful hardware and software, efficient cooling and lightning-fast connectivity, including Thunderbolt™ 4, 2.5 Gb and 1 Gb onboard Ethernet.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: ASUS is one of Fortune magazine’s World’s Most Admired Companies and is one of the top motherboard and gaming brands, as well as a top-three consumer notebook vendor. ASUS is driven by passion and innovation and dedicated to creating quality products for a future smart life, designing and manufacturing products that perfectly meet the needs of today's digital home, office and person. Our wide portfolio includes MG248Q, Chromebox and a range of devices and components, along with AR and VR. ProArt B760-CREATOR D4 ASUS ProArt B760-CREATOR D4 Intel LGA 1700 ATX motherboard, 12+1 power stages, DDR4, PCIe 5.0, three M.2 slots, 2.5 Gb & 1 Gb Ethernet, USB 3.2 Gen 2x2 Type-C front-panel connector, Thunderbolt (USB4) header Intel LGA 1700 Socket: Ready for 13th & 12th Gen Intel Core processors Comprehensive connectivity: 2.5 Gb & 1 Gb onboard Ethernet, three M.2 slots, Thunderbolt header support and a USB 3.2 Gen 2x2 front panel connector Next-gen performance: 12+1 power stages rated for 50 amps, PCIe 5.0 ready Optimized thermal design: A massive VRM and chipset heatsink, aluminum M.2 heatsinks, six 4-pin PWM fan headers and an AIO pump header ProArt gives you more: Two-Way AI Noise Cancelation for clear online communication and ProArt Creator Hub with CreationFirst for one-stop system control Advanced security management: USB port restriction, software blacklisting and Windows Registry protection via ASUS Control Center Express Free 3-month Adobe Creative Cloud Subscription: Receive complimentary access with the purchase of this product (offer valid from 9/15/2021 to 8/31/2024)

PCIe 5.0 for Graphics Cards The 13th Gen Intel processors offer PCIe 5.0 support, which offers twice the data transfer speed of PCIe 4.0, making it robust enough to handle new data-heavy tasks. PCIe 5.0 also brings other benefits such as improved signal integrity, backward-compatible CEM connectors for add-in cards and backward compatibility with previous PCIe versions. Dual Ethernet 2.5 Gb and 1 Gb Ethernet ports provide fast data transfers simultaneously for internet access and local network-attached storage (NAS), allowing for improved data organization and security.​ PCIe 4.0 M.2 Storage The ProArt B760-Creator D4 features three onboard M.2 slots, two of which are PCIe 4.0-ready for blistering speeds of up to 64 Gbps, while the third offers massive transfers of up to 32 Gbps through its PCIe 3.0 interface, enabling quicker boot-up and app load times with operating system or application drives.

Front USB3.2 Gen 2x2 Type-C A full complement of USB ports, including a front-panel USB 3.2 Gen 2x2 Type-C connector that provides data transfer speeds of up to 20 Gbps, supports high-end rigs loaded with peripherals.​ Thunderbolt / USB4 support The ProArt B760-Creator D4 features Thunderbolt 4 support via an on-board header. With an Intel-certified ASUS ThunderboltEX 4 add-on card*, this ProArt motherboard can enable bi-directional speeds of up to 40 Gbps on a single cable. Additionally, this card has a daisy-chain function for multiscreen connections, and it supports a display resolution of up to 8K. It can also provide up to 100 watts of power to fast-charge devices. *ASUS add-on card is sold separately.​ M.2 Slot (Key E) The ProArt B760-Creator D4 features an M.2 slot (key E) which can support type 2230 WiFi/Bluetooth modules*.​​ *WiFi/BT modules are sold separately.

Robust Power Design 12+1 Teamed Power Stages 12+1 teamed power stages Rated for 50 amps and combining high-side and low-side MOSFETs and drivers into a single package, these stages deliver power and efficiency tailored for the demands of​ the latest 13th & 12th Gen Intel Core processors.​ DDR4 Memory ProArt B760-Creator D4 supports up to 128 GB of DDR4 memory across four slots. ASUS-exclusive OptiMem II technology improves trace layout to significantly reduce signal distance and crosstalk, enhancing memory stability and compatibility while giving memory kits higher clock speed margins.​ Flexible Air- and Liquid-Cooling Controls ASUS Fan Xpert 4 software provides comprehensive control over fans, water pumps and all-in-one (AIO) coolers. Whether cooling with air or water, an Auto-Tuning mode intelligently configures all parameters with a single click. There’s also an Extreme Quiet mode that reduces all fan speeds to below the default minimum to keep your system whisper-quiet when performing light tasks. Fans, water pumps and AIO coolers can also be controlled via the UEFI BIOS.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good but get drivers from asus
reviews.reviewText: Good motherboard, but I had to install consumer intel chipset driver, intel lan driver, Intel sata driver, Intel ME driver, and intel IO driver from motherboard website. Also check ram compatibility and look up how to enable XMP properly had a BSOD because I didn’t enable XMP properly but everything is working.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Not For Inexperienced
reviews.reviewText: Not For Inexperienced. If you are considering assembling your own computer and you are not experienced in this task I would not recommend this MB since there is a dirth of information about this MB. The printed User Manual consists of 12 pages of basic rudimentary data. The on-line manual is essentially a repeat of the same info. The User Manual contains no information on the BIOS and states to contact ASUS support web site for BIOS info. There is no BIOS information on the web site. By comparison my ASUS X79 MB came with a 100+ page detailed assembling and BIOS data User Manual. The User Manual lists a number of software programs that are included with the MB. There is no CD/USB with the software included with the MB. A session with an ASUS Chat agent was unsatisfactory since he could not tell me where the software was or how to get it. There is a card titled, "ASUS Control Center Express" which requires scanning two QR codes to access the program and instructions. Not useful if you do not have a way to scan the QR codes. Final note - the advertisement for this MB states there is three months free access to Adobe Photoshop. There is no information on how to obtain this promotion.UPDATE. After a couple more unsuccessful emails with ASUS support to find the software just by chance I discovered that by clicking on the "Expand All" option at the top of "Driver" list the rest of the software that is included with the MB was displayed.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 15, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Creative Cloud Promotion Did Not Work
reviews.reviewText: The motherboard is pricey for what it features, however it does have Dual-LAN, a lot of USB ports, and two front panel connectors for USB. If you have an older case, buy a USB 3.1 connector/front panel with the appropriate header. The connectivity was the main reason to purchase this, along with the creative cloud bundle.The promo did not work using the Asus website. I tried using IE, Edge, and Firefox (with no extensions), and it failed each time. A customer support ticket has been submitted, but if you are looking to buy this motherboard for the offer as shown in the listing, just note that this purchase failed to activate using their website. Will update this review if the bundle works.

reviews.reviewTitle: Idéal pour faire du montage vidéo et des retouches photos.
reviews.reviewText: La Asus ProArt B660-Creator D4 est une carte mère améliorée conçue pour les charges de travail intensives liées à la création de contenu, comme le rendu 3D et l'édition vidéo 4K/8K. Il libère les performances des processeurs Intel Core de 12e génération grâce à une alimentation et un refroidissement robustes, tandis que sa connectivité complète comprend un Ethernet 2,5 Gb et 1 Gb embarqué, un connecteur avant USB 3.2 Gen 2x2 Type-C avec Quick Charge 4+, et DisplayPort via USB-C.
Ordered at 10pm and arrived by 10am next day. Well packaged, installed and performed as described.
